ndamental value of this token has increased,=E2=80=9D always =E2=80=9Cwe ca=
n sell this token to more people.=E2=80=9D It is a dispiriting sort of insi=
der trading.</p></blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">It is hard to ima=
