enerally, so I guess it makes sense that this case is about what got listed=
 on the homepage. But it does mean that no one was=C2=A0<em>deceived=C2=A0<=
/em>about the fundamental value of =E2=80=9CSpectrum of Ramenfication Theor=
y.=E2=80=9D If you bought it because you thought it was pretty, and then so=
ld it to this guy because you=E2=80=99d rather have the money, him putting =
it on OpenSea=E2=80=99s homepage doesn=E2=80=99t change the basic nature of=
 the transaction.=C2=A0</p><table class=3D"liveintent-sponsored-content" wi=
